	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="">Question???</a> <a id="fs8" href="#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Wed, Dec 18th 8:09 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=79142"><span id=" ">The One and Only Millroygreat</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">11 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Anyone want to explain to me how the Bonus Dmg works on a weapon?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Fettena 68 Druid<br/>~Watchers~<br/>Brell Server</td></tr>
